<article>
    <h1>Lavo&#x2019;s Sun&#xAD;day Cham&#xAD;pagne Brunch</h1>
    <h2></h2>
    <section>
        <a href="/singapore/the-straits-times/textview" title="The Straits Times">The Straits Times</a>
        - <a href="/singapore/the-straits-times/20200911/textview" title="The Straits Times - 2020-09-11"><time>2020-09-11</time></a>
        - <span>LIFE</span>
        - <span role="byline"></span>
    </section>

    <p>Lavo Ital­ian Restau­rant & Rooftop Bar is bring­ing back its Sun­day Cham­pagne Brunch, which has been re­vamped and is now served a la carte. For $88++ a per­son, din­ers can en­joy a free flow of items such as Truf­fled Crab Salad, Wagyu Meat­ball Pizza and Prime Hanger Steak. For $158++ a per­son, the food can be paired with a free flow of Veuve Clic­quot cham­pagne, spe­cial­ity cock­tails and other bev­er­ages.</p>
    <p>There is also a one-for-one pro­mo­tion on cock­tails and pas­tas un­til Sept 20; avail­able daily from 10pm to mid­night for pas­tas, and 3 to 7pm for cock­tails. Din­ers are en­cour­aged to post a pic­ture of their one-for-one dish or cock­tail on In­sta­gram with a cre­ative cap­tion and the hash­tag #LAVOLovesY­ou, and tag @LavoSin­ga­pore. Two en­tries will win a pair of tick­ets to the Sun­day Cham­pagne Brunch.</p>
    <p>WHERE: Lavo Ital­ian Restau­rant And Rooftop Bar, Level 57 Ma­rina Bay Sands Tower 1, 10 Bayfront Av­enue MRT: Bayfront WHEN: Sun, noon - 3pm TEL: Reser­va­tions re­quired.</p>
    <p>Call 6688-8591 or e-mail lavo.reser­va­tions@ marin­abaysands.com</p>
    <p>face­book.com/LavoSin­ga­pore</p>


</article>

